  "prompt": "How can I report someone on Quora?",
  "response": "If you want to report someone on Quora, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Go to the Profile**: Visit the profile of the person you want to report.\n\n2. **Find the Report Option**: Look for the three-dot menu (`...`) usually located near the user's name or profile picture on their profile page.\n\n3. **Select 'Report'**: Click on the three-dot menu and select the 'Report' option from the dropdown menu.\n\n4. **Choose a Reason**: Quora will likely present you with several reasons for the report, such as spam, harassment, fake profile, etc. Select the one that best fits the issue.\n\n5. **Submit the Report**: Follow any additional prompts to submit the report.\n\nQuora's moderation team will review the report and take action if necessary. It's important to report users only for legitimate reasons and in accordance with Quora's policies.",
